                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6991" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1096</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8862 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小小面条，也绕不过STP—谷峰尚品标准化鲜面的差异化突围之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Even a small noodle factory cannot bypass STP ——ACE-NOODLES rely on differentiation to break through the dilemma</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">景涛，张建勇，李依潼</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春市荣和丰食品有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP；目标市场营销；定位；差异化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP; Target&#160;marketing&#160;strategy; Positioning; Differentiation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例跟踪描摹了一家小型面条企业曲折跌宕的6年创业历程。主人公携其创立的“谷峰尚品”半干面品牌，作为行业小白，懵懂闯入了面条批量加工行业。原以为门槛不高、需求广阔，不料甫一入手，错漏百出、难以为继。直到两年前偶然转型鲜面生产，继而打入连锁面馆供应链，方得绝处逢生。随后顺势扩大代工战果，试水终端零售。面对全新挑战，“谷峰尚品”为突破自身认知局限引入外脑。专家开出了“以STP战略创新为魂，开辟‘标准化鲜面’蓝海，打造‘精制标准化鲜面专家’全新定位，以差异化整合化营销组合开创全新局面”的药方。这条从自发到自觉的转型突围之路会走向何方？令人充满期待……案例旨在建立对STP（尤市场定位）这一营销核心精华理论的内涵、意义、逻辑框架及方法工具的深刻认知。同时俯瞰STP上承下接的战略枢纽地位，加深对营销管理过程框架内在逻辑的理解。此外，让学生直观感受如何应用理论科学化、体系化地分析和解决问题，体验其中超越经验的逻辑快感，进而提升理论学习的信心和自觉。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the 6-year tortuous entrepreneurial process of a small noodle enterprise. The protagonist of the story, with his &quot; ACE-NOODLES &quot; semi dry noodle brand, as a newcomer in the industry, recklessly broke into the daily necessities industry of noodle processing. The advantage of this project is that the entry threshold is not high and the demand is broad. Unexpectedly, from the beginning, he fell into constant difficulties and troubles. The company&#39;s development has stalled. It was not until two years ago that he began to transform fresh noodle production due to an accidental opportunity, and then entered the supply chain of chain noodle restaurants that the brand regained its vitality. Then he took advantage of the trend to expand his business and began to enter the terminal retail market. In order to meet the new challenge, &quot; ACE-NOODLES &quot; introduces the external brain to get advice. The solution given by the experts is to take STP strategic innovation as the soul, open up a blue ocean of &quot;standardized fresh noodles&quot;, create a new market positioning of &quot;refined standardized fresh noodles expert&quot;, and create a new situation with differentiated marketing strategy. Where will this transition road eventually go? It is full of expectation. This case aims to establish a deep understanding of the connotation, significance, logical framework, methods and tools of STP marketing strategy theory. At the same time, guide students to overlook the strategic hub position of STP, and deepen their understanding of the system framework of marketing management process. In addition, let students understand how to apply theory to analyze and solve problems scientifically and systematically, experience the logical pleasure beyond experience, and then improve their confidence and consciousness in theoretical learning.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销管理》、《企业营销策划》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP理论；营销环境+购买行为+需求测量预测；4P营销组合理论；营销管理过程框架</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
